The paper deals with the problem of specifying and verifying quantified queries in databases, which is a core topic in the field of database management systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes algorithms for learning and verifying these queries, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The paper uses mathematical analysis and optimization techniques, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG) and algorithms (cs.DS).
